Torrent Reader
------------------
Author : Guillaume Dorion-Racine
Email  : gdorion@gmail.com

Description : 
This app load a .torrent file and presents it's metadata information to the user.
Press the '+' button to open and load the a file.

The files contained in the torrent will be shown in the table view.

The torrent files that are under a folder will be presented like this : 
SampleFolder/Myfile.mp4

Ref.:
https://wiki.theory.org/BitTorrentSpecification
http://www.bittorrent.org/beps/bep_0003.html

